A JVM-based Erlang VM:

http://www.erjang.org
https://github.com/trifork/erjang

How to run:

$ cd .../osv-apps/erjang

$ capstan build
Building erjang...
Downloading cloudius/osv-openjdk/index.yaml...
149 B / 149 B [=========================================================================================] 100.00 % 
Downloading cloudius/osv-openjdk/osv-openjdk.qemu.gz...
60.80 MB / 60.80 MB [===================================================================================] 100.00 % 

$ capstan run
Created instance: erjang
OSv v0.09
eth0: 192.168.122.15
** Erjang R16B01 **  [root:/~resource] [erts:5.10.2] [smp S:1 A:10] [java:1.7.0_51] [unicode]
Eshell V5.10.2  (abort with ^G)
